WEBVTT 

00:00:01.080 --> 00:00:03.480
The truck has to be washed!

00:00:03.560 --> 00:00:07.920
-Find out first where...
-Go and open the boom barrier.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:10.640
-I'm not allowed.
-Go!

00:00:10.720 --> 00:00:12.520
I will explain once more.

00:00:12.600 --> 00:00:16.240
And I'm saying the truck can't
leave the car park without a wash!

00:00:16.320 --> 00:00:20.600
...when it arrives to the car park!

00:00:20.680 --> 00:00:24.800
I'm telling you. I saw him coming here.

00:00:24.880 --> 00:00:29.560
I saw clearly where he came from
and where he unloaded.

00:00:29.640 --> 00:00:32.800
Go on and do it again!

